svg></a></span>，可能是因为进化出两个性别比进化出三个性别在各种方面都容易的多叭，<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=149438286&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%9F%93%E8%89%B2%E4%BD%93&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">染色体<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>都是成对的嘛。。。（当然这是反推，真的要有理有据的解释它的话我也不知道为什么....</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
